{"tid":907524,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有傳中聯辦下令，禁止建制派去台灣觀選。","createTime":"2018-11-19T00:28:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-19T16:25:41.000Z","uid":1886,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"0773d35cc4b8709d340ae610b01cf11c692f59a0","tid":907524,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T00:28:00.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181118/large/1542541476_6274.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181118%2Flarge%2F1542541476_6274.jpg&h=d577f50e&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n台灣九合一選舉將於本周六（24日）舉行，過去不論泛民同建制嘅政界人士都專程到當地觀摩選舉活動，但今年香港建制派嘅觀選意慾，似乎大大減低，有建制派同八方講，中聯辦認為而家台海關係緊張，已經向本港嘅建制派發出「硬命令」，唔希望佢哋去台灣觀選，更加有人講到，中聯辦其實係想佢哋「連台灣都唔好去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」。嘩，使唔使封殺得咁緊要呀？<br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181118/58927800\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181118%2F58927800&d=pZBVOThsalqHuy22W8pBzJZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=86126d95\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181118%2F58927800&h=c4cb7fdc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181118/58927800</a>"},{"pid":"175003194eb4e47d3a757a02ab23ea834294431b","tid":907524,"uid":1886,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T00:29:03.000Z","msg":"每次台灣大選，本港嘅政團都會透過陸委會安排到台灣觀戰，一來感受下選舉氣氛，二來亦可以參考下喺台灣嘅選舉制度下，候選人係點樣宣傳同拉票。好似2016年台灣大選民主動力同新思維等政團就組團觀選，而現任議員民建聯陳恒鑌同埋資深建制派工聯會陳婉嫻都有去觀摩。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181118/large/1542520755_17cd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181118%2Flarge%2F1542520755_17cd.jpg&h=24782cf6&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n台灣本周又會有九合一大選，但八方打聽過，呢次冇乜建制派赴台觀選，事關西環早前已經發出硬指令，要求建制派唔好去台灣，消息話，唔止現役建制派議員，退下火線嘅「頭面人物」亦不獲放行，只有部分建制出身嘅學者可以獲得豁免。消息又話，中聯辦方面無明言原因，但相信係因為近日台海關係緊張所致；至於係「永久禁止」定係「一次性」？情況一如被DQ嘅議員係咪永久不能參選一樣，完全冇講明囉！"},{"pid":"37b09f1f02c089c56f63e5944504615a39fe44a5","tid":907524,"uid":4942,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T00:33:14.000Z","msg":"玻璃心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be372dac23f1f29082d0d72bdbe17dbaf0781487","tid":907524,"uid":50457,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T00:41:22.000Z","msg":"香港人享有出入境的自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n中國是最自由的國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一國&ldquo;兩制&rdquo;無變形，無走樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af4b6b92e33c0fd89e121afebb38bb6bdd18d7e4","tid":907524,"uid":47674,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T01:04:47.000Z","msg":"快啲禁埋支那人民去台灣"},{"pid":"bcc4f9267dc971f0a51a9241c8502a718f37a261","tid":907524,"uid":4942,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T01:06:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>快啲禁埋支那人民去台灣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n快啲禁埋支那人民去日本"},{"pid":"298075774b5f3d2d94358dc39bba07be22b28ff4","tid":907524,"uid":122677,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"bcc4f9267dc971f0a51a9241c8502a718f37a261","tid":907524,"uid":4942,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T01:06:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>快啲禁埋支那人民去台灣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n快啲禁埋支那人民去日本"},"citedBy":